|date=30 May 2014| accessdate=16 August 2014|work=The Times of India}}</ref> 

2010 vorsamni tachea chhapkhaneacho khorch mellovpak jairati mellovp, tea masikacho mukhel prosn aslo.<ref name="Noronha" />

Tacho sthapnnar [[Lambert Mascarenhas]],<ref>{{Cite journal|author=Qasim, Seeme|year=2007|title=Inward Journeys|journal=India International Centre Quarterly|volume=34|issue=1|pages=84–96|jstor=23006049}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|author=Nazareth, Peter|year=1985|title=Alienation, nostalgia, and homecoming: editing an anthology of Goan literature|journal=World Literature Today|volume=59|issue=3|pages=374–382|jstor=40140844}}</ref> aslo zannem atam piraiechi xotabdi olanddlea.<ref name="Noronha" /><ref>{{Cite news |title=To-be-centenarian Lambert Mascarenhas |date=August 2014 |newspaper=GoaCom |url=http://www.goacom.com/snapshots/1188-to-be-centenarian-lambert-mascarenhas |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RmRUomxX?url=http://www.goacom.com/snapshots/1188-to-be-centenarian-lambert-mascarenhas |archivedate=12 August 2014 |deadurl=no |df= }}</ref> Mascarenhas hachea uprant [[Vaman Sardesai]] tacho sompadok aslo, zannem tem pod Bharotacho Angolak Rajdut zalo ten’na soddlem.<ref>{{Cite news|author=de Souza, Teotónio Rosário|date=12 November 2008|title=Dishonouring Our Freedom Fighters|newspaper=The Herald|location=Goa|volume=108|issue=317|page=8|url=http://recil.grupolusofona.pt/xmlui/bitstream/handle/10437/523/Herald_121108.pdf|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812193043/http://recil.grupolusofona.pt/xmlui/bitstream/handle/10437/523/Herald_121108.pdf|archivedate=12 August 2014|deadurl=no}}</ref> Uprant Manohar Shetty hea kovi-sompadokan tem pod duxoilem zannem tachem unchlem promann dovorlem ani Goenchem sahiteo porgottlem zantunt tannem itihas, rajkornni prosn ani sahiteo hancho tall-mell dovorlo.<ref>{{Cite book|author=Kumar, Shiv|year=2008|chapter=One Outsider Looks In|editor=Noronha, Frederick|title=Behind the News: Voices from Goa's Press|publisher=Goa 1556|location=Goa|pages=141–142|isbn=978-81-905682-0-3}}</ref> Vinayak Naik atam tacho sompadok asa.<ref name="Noronha" />

